main event: Two oval-shaped objects were sighted in Lake City, Tennessee on November 20, 1955.
interesting points: The objects were described as white and yellow, resembling dirigibles without sound,The sighting lasted between 4 to 15 minutes,During the sighting, the objects showed erratic flight, moving against the wind,One observer described the objects as being brighter than the background sky and compared them to a half-dollar,Multiple witnesses including military personnel reported similar observations of the objects.
witness description: Military personnel and a civilian telephone company manager
